visual_description.name: outdoor_garden_cafe_seating.jpg
visual_description.description: White wooden tables and chairs scattered on green lawn. Purple tree provides shade. Bright daylight, some shadowing. Background: car, playground, red wooden structure. Slightly cluttered arrangement.
visual_description.score_basis: Pleasant outdoor cafe setting, vibrant greens. Some shadow disruption, high contrast. Table placement appears crowded, limiting space. High-resolution, natural colors, not fake. Mildly inviting but visually busy.
visual_description.purpose: Outdoor cafe or event seating promotion.
